==================
ResourceSync Tools 
==================

  * ``resync-stats`` - Make a one-pager of stats for a ResourceSync site

Requirements - OSX
------------------

The `Matplotlib
<http://matplotlib.org/index.html>`_ backends need python to be installed as a "framework" in order to interact with the native GUI. See `Working with Matplotlib on OSX
<http://matplotlib.org/faq/osx_framework.html#osxframework-faq>`_ for details.

For example, using ``Conda`` one must install with ``conda install python.app`` and use ``pythonw`` instead of ``python``, e.g.::

    pythonw resync-stats -r my_resource_list.xml

